OL,5, Citibank has won an employment tribunal
OL,6, after sacking a worker for claiming    
OL,7, expenses for sandwiches and coffee for 
OL,8, his partner, and then lying about it.  
OL,10,FSzabolcs Fekete had accused the bank of
OL,11,Funfair dismissal after he was fired    
OL,12,Flast year for gross misconduct.        
OL,14,FMr Fekete had initially claimed that he
OL,15,Falone had consumed two sandwiches, two 
OL,16,Fcoffees and two pasta dishes during a  
OL,17,Fbusiness trip to Amsterdam.            
OL,19,FBut he later admitted that his partner 
OL,20,Fhad shared some meals.                 
